CREATED:20260322T230749Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260322T230749Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Lancaster Freethought Society
UID:event_314167936@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260408T030353Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260418T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260418T120000
SUMMARY:LFS Walk in the Park!
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Freethought Society\nJust a hike around the park\, e
 njoying the weather!\n\nConsider bringing water and snacks. Wear appropria
 te shoes\, bring water shoes if you would like to wade in the river. Sunsc
 reen recommended. Mix of paved trails and dirt trails\, some trails might 
 require a moderate climb. This event is pet-friendly! The park offers rest
 room facilities. In the event of weather we'll instead meet at Pavilion 1 
 and chat!\n\nAfter crossing the Strawberry St. bridge over the Conestoga r
 iver to enter the park\, there is a parking lot downhill to the left (pict
 ured above). We'll meet\, pick a route\, and walk!\n\n(If you have difficu
 lty finding the spot on GPS\, try: 38 Pontz Dr\, Lancaster\, PA 17602)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-freethought-society/events/
 314167936/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260407T184039Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260407T184039Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Lancaster Freethought Society
UID:event_308585161@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260408T030353Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260419T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260419T120000
SUMMARY:LFS Coffee & Convo  
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Freethought Society\nThe Coffee and Convo meetup is 
 always on the 3rd Sunday of the Month at 9am.\n\nWe will meet at Centervil
 le Diner\, 100 S. Centerville Rd.\n\nMeet up with fellow freethinkers to t
 alk\, eat or just have a warm or cold beverage of your choice. This is usu
 ally a small intimate meeting. It's about casual conversation and getting 
 to know your fellow freethinkers.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-freethought-society/events/
 308585161/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20250621T185228Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20250621T185228Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
