DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260425T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260425T210000
SUMMARY:Evening Discussion and Dinner!
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Freethought Society\nEnjoy dinner and discussion at 
 Indian Curry Lounge with us\, 6:00pm\, Saturday April 25th!\n\nYou may rem
 ember this Indian restaurant location was previously known as Namaste\, an
 d before that Tulsi. It is built into the first floor of the motel buildin
 g\, it is two doors down from El Serranos\, where we meet for our other mo
 nthly evening meeting!\n\nIndian Curry Lounge\n2101 Columbia Avenue\nLanca
 ster PA 17603
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-freethought-society/events/
 314167949/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260407T184154Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260407T184154Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Lancaster Freethought Society
UID:event_308585166@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260408T030353Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260506T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260506T210000
SUMMARY:LFS Monthly Discussion - El Serrano's
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Freethought Society\nCome joins us for intelligent d
 iscussion and freethinking fun at our monthly meeting. Lancaster Freethoug
 ht Society is a community for Freethinkers\, Atheists\, Agnostics\, Humani
 sts\, Non-believers\, Skeptics\, and those who are simply curious. There i
 s no fee to attend our meetings which range from topical subjects of inter
 est to freethinkers such as Church/State Separation\, as well as subjects 
 such as science\, philosophy\, ethics\, counter-apologetics\, and psycholo
 gy. All are welcome to attend no matter what your beliefs may be but prose
 lytizing is not allowed. Bring your articles\, news\, jokes\, gripes\, que
 stions\, ideas\, topics\, or anything else you would like to discuss with 
 the rest of the group.\n\nHope to see you there!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-freethought-society/events/
 308585166/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20250621T185239Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20250621T185239Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
